headline: Varied Growth Drivers Led ClearBridge Investments Growth Strategy to Add The Sherwin-Williams Company (SHW)
summary: ClearBridge Investments, an investment management company, released its “ClearBridge Growth Strategy” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. US equities significantly rallied in the second quarter, with the S&P 500 returning 10.9%.
